node.text: Epic hold and an even more epic face. Just another day on the ole pond getting guided by @kyleborgschatz

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jonathan Barzacchini on July 11, 2021 tagging @wyatt_morse14, and @grant_langmore7. May be an image of 3 people and outdoors.

node.text: It has been a smallmouth filled week up here in Maine. @grant_langmore7 and I  have chased down stripers, fished 7 different lakes and competed in the second Maine derb of the season all in a matter of a few days. I know I’ve been lacking on the uploads but just know the best is coming. Thank you wieners for being patient 🙏🏻

node.text: Smashing hybrids with this cute thang. After popping a few  meat heads off @kayleighg__ finally winched a couple of good ones in. When the largies are being lame you can always count on the stripies bois to crush.
